${C_BOLD}INVESTIGATION AREAS${C_RESET}
    â€¢ Package manager caches (pacman, npm, cargo, pip)
    â€¢ System logs and journal data
    â€¢ Docker containers, images, and build cache
    â€¢ Temporary files and crash dumps
